'''傑諾德·懷茲勒'''（Jerrold Wexler，{{bd|1924年|6月27日|1992年|11月10日}}），是一位美國商人。他是[[Haskell_Wexler|Haskell Wexler]]的哥哥也是 [[戴露·漢娜|戴露·漢娜]]的繼父。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lycos.com/info/daryl-hannah--jerrold-wexler.html |title=Daryl Hannah: Jerrold Wexler |publisher=Lycos Inc. |accessdate=2007-11-07 |date=2007 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20070707024634/http://www.lycos.com/info/daryl-hannah--jerrold-wexler.html |archivedate=2007-07-07 }}</ref>

他30年前以建造紀念摩天大樓聞名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,809078,00.html|title=Business and Technology section|publisher=Time Inc.|work=Time Magazine|accessdate=2007-11-08|date=1957-02-11|archive-date=2013-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130811214818/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,809078,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 自1979年開始他和他的商業伙伴 Edward W. Ross, 買下了 [[:en:Drake_Hotel_(Chicago)|達克旅館]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://thedrakehotel.com/pdf/press_kit.pdf |accessdate=2007-11-07 |publisher=thedrakehotel.com |title=Press Kit 2007 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061113021214/http://www.thedrakehotel.com/pdf/press_kit.pdf |archivedate=2006-11-13 }}</ref>1980年達克成為美国[[:en:National_Register_of_Historic_Place|國家級歷史性建築]]。1983年 Wexler將興趣移轉到[[:en:Playboy_Building|玩伴女郎大楼]]、湖心塔（[[:en:Lake_Point_Tower|Lake Point Tower]]）、[[密西根大街_(芝加哥)|密西根大街]]的建築房地，數以打計的芝加哥旅館，他還在在紐約市和洛杉磯置產，救助了當時即將破產的 [[Goldblatt's|Goldblatt's]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fundinguniverse.com/company-histories/JG-Industries-Inc-Company-History.html|title=JG Industries, Inc.|accessdate=2007-11-07|publisher=fundinguniverse.com|archive-date=2012-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419125520/http://www.fundinguniverse.com/company-histories/JG-Industries-Inc-Company-History.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>  當[[Bertram_Lee|Bertram Lee]] 在10%的併購案失敗之後failed to come up with his ten percent share to purchase the [[National_Basketball_Association|National Basketball Association]] [[Denver_Nuggets|Denver Nuggets]] in 1989, [[Peter_Bynoe|Peter Bynoe]] recruited Jerrold Wexler and [[Jay_Pritzker|Jay Pritzker]] 讓生意繼續保持活絡。這個團隊在1992年以很大的興趣 [[COMSAT|COMSAT]] 買下了 [[Drexel_Burnham_Lambert|Drexel Burnham Lambert]]銀行, Bynoe 和他的夥伴們。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fundinguniverse.com/company-histories/Denver-Nuggets-Company-History.html|title=Denver Nuggets|accessdate=2007-11-07|publisher=fundinguniverse.com|archive-date=2012-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120121112849/http://www.fundinguniverse.com/company-histories/Denver-Nuggets-Company-History.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>除了他在商業上的興趣之外，他也是一名活耀的政治獻金捐助者。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.newsmeat.com/fec/bystate_detail.php?zip=60611&last=WEXLER&first=JERROLD |title=CAMPAIGN CONTRIBUTION SEARCH (individual donations of $200 or more since 1978): JERROLD WEXLER » IL » 60611 |accessdate=2007-11-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604073302/http://www.newsmeat.com/fec/bystate_detail.php?zip=60611&last=WEXLER&first=JERROLD |archivedate=2011-06-04 }}</ref>  In addition此外, 他同時也是John Austin Cheley 基金會的受託人。.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cheleyfoundation.org/boardof.htm |accessdate=2007-11-09 |date=2007-10-01 |title=Organization |publisher=John Austin Cheley Foundation |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070607150505/http://www.cheleyfoundation.org/boardof.htm |archivedate=2007-06-07 }}</ref>

